title: Ep 1876 - A Twist in The Story
shortDesc: Dhanraj chinor, the jeweller who had lost his box of gold biscuits goes to police station a registers a complaint to find his box. The inspector on hearing that his mobile is missing asks the number & starts his investigation.

title: Ep 1877 - Police complaint against Bhide
shortDesc: Police crew reached Gokuldham Society to find Bhide and arrest him thinking that he is the thief. As they enter Bhide' s house they see all the members of the society. They assume everyone as a gang of thieves

title: Ep 1878 - Bhide gets arrested
shortDesc: The Jeweller refuses to believe the incident explained by Bhide. All his friends also explain that he is innocent. But Dhanraj asks why he didn't go to police station to return the gold last night if he really was innocent

title: Ep 1879 - Bhide Ki Azaadi
shortDesc: Bhide is arrested on an allegation of stealing briefcase full of gold. However, Bhide’s friends were devising a plan to take him out from the lockup. They were tensed and were trying their best to prove him innocent before Court!

title: Ep 1880 - Popatlals Plan to Trap Dhanraj
shortDesc: Popatlal has devised a plan to trap Seth Dhanraj and for this he has dressed up like a rich businessman who has a very big business of Gold in Jodhpur. However, he met Seth Dhanraj and offered him a business deal.

title: Ep 1881 - Bhide Bachao Mission Begins
shortDesc: The mission to prove Bhide innocent has started by the men of Gokuldham society. Jethalal and others were executing their plans extremely well to trap Dhanraj Seth!

title: Ep 1882 - Proof against Dhanraj
shortDesc: The mission of Jethalal and his friends to free Bhide from the jail has become successful. They have tried to recreate the same situation which Bhide might have faced on that particular night.

title: Ep 1883 - Bhides tour to Lockup
shortDesc: Jethalal and his friends were very happy that they have accumulated sufficient evidences to prove Bhide innocent before inspector Chalu Pandey. However, on the other hand Dhanraj Seth is completely prepared

title: Ep 1884 - Dayas Mission
shortDesc: All the attempts of Jethalal and his friends to prove Bhide innocent before inspector Chalu Pandey has gone into vain. And now, it’s not only Bhide but Jethalal and others were too locked up inside the police station

title: Ep 1885 - Vital Clue in Bhides Case
shortDesc: Everyone in Gokuldham Society was tensed after the arrest of Bhide, Jethalal and their friends on various allegation levelled against them. However, after a brief discussion Daya struck upon an idea that the taxi driver could help them

title: Ep 1886 - Bhide Proved Innocent
shortDesc: Bhide and all of his friends were inside the lockup on allegations of stealing the briefcase full of gold. However, the Mahila Mandal of Gokuldham Society have devised a plan to prove them innocent

title: Ep 1887 - Chalu Pandey at Bhides House
shortDesc: Bhide and his friends who were proved innocent in gold theft case were now feeling easy and were experiencing the freedom in their life. However, they were released from the Lockup but very soon Chalu Pandey

title: Ep 1888 - Aabhar Ke Phool
shortDesc: Bhide and all his friends were proven innocent in the gold briefcase theft case. However, to thank the residents of Gokuldham Society and his friends for supporting him in such a difficult situation, Bhide and Madhvi planned to meet them personally

title: Ep 1889 - Champaklal Ka Suvichar
shortDesc: Bhide the secretary of Gokuldham Society was trying to write a thought of the day on the notice board of the society but sadly nothing was striking in his mind. However, it was Champaklal who has suggested a very valuable thought to Bhide and other

title: Ep 1890 - Bawris Concern
shortDesc: Jethalal was busy in his work but it was then Bagha interrupted him is in own style to insist him for a cup of tea. However, the very next moment Bawri came rushing down to Gada Electronics and to meet Bagha to discuss something important!
